Aylin based on Codeigniter and use other third party useful library to create an easy and rapid web development.
for more information , bug report and partnership please join to :
aylincms@googlegroups.com

INSTALLATION
====================
copy source to web server directory
create a database
change owner of source to webserver user, for example:
  in  slackware:
    chown -R apache:apache aylin/
  id debian:
    chown -R www-data:www-data aylin/
and run install folder inside of AylinCMS in web browser

